## RegisterOptions.force property

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

If true, overwrites existing capabilities with the same fully-qualified ID. Defaults to false (first-registered wins).

